=== Causes of Abortion

==== 1st Trimester Causes
#viva
- Chromosomal abnormalities
- Infections (TORCH, malaria)
- Endocrine causes (DM, hypothyroidism, luteal defect)
- Maternal systemic illness
- Drugs, radiation

#high_yeild
- *Genetic:* Chromosomal abnormalities (especially autosomal trisomy) cause ~50% of early losses.

==== 2nd Trimester Causes
#viva
- Cervical incompetence
- Uterine anomalies (bicornuate/septate uterus)
- Maternal infections (syphilis, listeria)
- Placental causes
- Trauma

#high_yeild
- *Anatomical:* Cervical incompetence, bicornuate uterus.

